patthana16.42:1.1_0: Paccuppanno hetu dhammo naatītassa nahetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. Paccuppanno
patthana16.42:1.1_1: hetu dhammo naanāgatassa nahetussa dhammassa hetupaccayena paccayo. Paccuppanno hetu
patthana16.42:1.1_2: dhammo naatītassa nahetussa ca naanāgatassa nahetussa ca dhammassa hetupaccayena
patthana16.42:1.1_3: paccayo. (Saṅkhittaṁ.) Hetuyā tīṇi, ārammaṇe nava, adhipatiyā cha, anantare tīṇi
